messages.title: A strong voice for you
messages.content: A vote for me on June 8th will give you a strong voice in Parliament. I'll be an MP who will make sure Brexit is delivered AND that you get the better life you deserve.

leaflet.personalStatement: A vote for me on June 8th will give you a strong voice in Parliament. I'll be an MP who will make sure Brexit is delivered AND that you get the better life you deserve.
